      "content": "rebuilding? how can you even say that? i'm talking about millions in debt and a reputation that's basically dead. there is no \"rebuilding\" from this. once you've failed this hard, everyone sees you for what you are. the shame isn't just a feeling, it's my entire reality now. it feels like there's no version of the future where this isn't just hanging over me forever. it's just... an endless loop of failure.",
